release_note: This 5.0 version release presents major improvements over transcription accuracy along other improvements: AI powered transcription Overall UI updated to iOS 17 patterns Overall performance improvements Enjoy!
iOS 16 major update includes new features such as Widgets. Bug fixes and stability improvements

Support for MP4 files. Bug fixes and stability improvements.

Voice to Text Pro was redesigned from the ground up using the newest Apple technology and APIs. We rewrote the base structure of the app to support the new features we are planning to include in future releases. New features in this release: A new and more modern UI. You can finally pause transcriptions and resume them! A lot of bug fixes and under the hood improvements.
Fixed: Some users were having issues trying to delete their notes. Fixed: Some users had multiple notes created when AutoSave Notes was enabled.

We are proud to present Voice to Text 3.0 to users coming with plenty of new features check it out: New design the whole experience has been redesigned from the ground. We will love to hear your feedback. Widgets taking advantage of full capabilities of the new iOS 14 Improved transcription Custom dictionary add frequently used word to improve transcription accuracy Larger text. Another feature to improve app accessibility And more...
Improved translations! We ve improved all translations for better accuracy please let us know if there are still any issues.
Improvements to the UI: now the app has tabs for easy access to the most used screens.
Light theme! Now you can toggle between light and dark modes in Settings. Dictation guide with common commands you can say.

Transcription of external audio files! We heard your feedback and now you have the option to transcribe external audio files. You can access them directly inside Voice to Text Pro ou share audio files from any app installed on your device.
Notes creation: now you ll have a place to store your notes create new ones based on your transcriptions or append text to existing notes!

Bug fixes and stability improvements We release updates regularly and we re always looking for ways to make things better. Feel free to rate and leave a review if the app is important for you it helps a lot. And if you have any feedback or run into issues please contact us via hugo.prione gmail.com. We re happy to help!
